groundhog.description: Punxsutawney Phil is a superstar prognosticating groundhog from Punxsutawney, Pennsylvania. He makes his predictions from his burrow on Goblers Knob. According to legend, Phil has made weather prognostications since 1886, owing his improbably long life to the miraculous groundhog nog administered at the annual Groundhog Picnic.
groundhog.name: Punxsutawney Phil

groundhog.description: Lucy the Lobster makes Groundhog Day predictions on February 2nd to kick off the Lobster Crawl festival in Barrington, Nova Scotia. The Municipality of Barrington says Lucy is the only prognosticating crustacean to make a prediction in Canada. Bill Murray was reported as being bemused by the idea of a lobster forecaster.
groundhog.name: Lucy the Lobster

example-1.description: Punxsutawney Phil is a superstar prognosticating groundhog from Punxsutawney, Pennsylvania. He makes his predictions from his burrow on Goblers Knob. According to legend, Phil has made weather prognostications since 1886, owing his improbably long life to the miraculous groundhog nog administered at the annual Groundhog Picnic.
example-1.name: Punxsutawney Phil

predictions.details: No Shadow- Early Spring It was 28 at Gobblers Knob. Phil made his perdition of an Early Spring at 7:25 a.m.
7:25 a.m. Saw His Shadow, Six More Weeks of Winter! There were a few snow flurries during the prognostication.
At 7:25 a.m. with 18,000 Phil Phans present, Phil saw his shadow! Six More Weeks of Winter!
NO Shadow at 7:28 AM; 14 fog & mist with -1 Wind Chill.
NO Shadow at 7:26 AM; 30 with light snow falling.
Shadow at 7:25 AM; 19 with light snow. Coronavirus fear prohibits crowds on Gobblers Knob.
Shadow at 7:27 AM; 27 with clear skies. A loyal crowd of thousands returned to Gobblers Knob.

example-1.description: Lucy the Lobster makes Groundhog Day predictions on February 2nd to kick off the Lobster Crawl festival in Barrington, Nova Scotia. The Municipality of Barrington says Lucy is the only prognosticating crustacean to make a prediction in Canada. Bill Murray was reported as being bemused by the idea of a lobster forecaster.
example-1.name: Lucy the Lobster
